<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">This sample illustrates how to serialize or de-serialize OlapReport settings along with the appearance of OlapGrid control, such as its column header, row header, summary cells and cell border.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">The following customizations are used to demonstrate this sample:</Paragraph>

<List MarkerStyle="Disc" Margin="20,25,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Background</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Column Header</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Row Header</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Summary Cell</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Font Settings</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Font Family</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14" FontWeight="Bold">Font Color</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem></List>

<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"><Image Source="images/SerializationDemo.png" Stretch="None"/></Paragraph>

</Section>

